"    STRUCTURALLY INDEPENDENT — meta's consciousness depends" . cr
"    only on its own out-degree to children plus self-loop." . cr
"    Children's individual Φ_PA values do NOT contribute." . cr
"    Verified invariant across children's Φ_PA from 20000 to" . cr
"    200000 (10× range)." . cr
cr
"  phi-perc(M) ~ Σ comp-size(O_i)" . cr
"    CONNECTIVITY-INHERITED — meta's percolation-Φ grows with" . cr
"    total reachable nodes, including all sub-observer leaves." . cr
"    Φ_perc(M) = 16 · L_max for 3 sub-observers with 4 leaves" . cr
"    each (meta + 3 subs + 12 leaves)." . cr
cr
"Consequence for combination problem:" . cr
"  - phi-pa: REJECTS additive panpsychism; meta consciousness" . cr
"    is structural, not inherited" . cr
"  - phi-perc: SUPPORTS connectivity-additive panpsychism;" . cr
"    meta consciousness aggregates reachability" . cr
cr
"Substrate-derived: different measures → different combination" . cr
"resolutions.  The combination problem in substrate-monism is" . cr
"MEASURE-DEPENDENT, not absolute." . cr

REPORT
